ValueSet: EMICounselingStatusVS
Id: emi-counseling-status-vs
Title: "EMI Counseling Status Value Set"
Description: "Value set for medication counseling status responses (yes, no, not applicable, etc.)."

* ^status = #active

* EMICounselingStatusCS#yes "Yes"
* EMICounselingStatusCS#no "No"
* EMICounselingStatusCS#not-applicable "Not Applicable"
* EMICounselingStatusCS#refused "Refused"
* EMICounselingStatusCS#unknown "Unknown"
